user.biography:
Your go-to destination for men’s style inspo and fashion tips. 
🔥 We love your style! Tag @HM_man and #HMMan for a chance to be featured on our feed.

node.text: Join this year's guest designer Giambattista Valli and his friends as they prepare for the red carpet at the amfAR gala in Cannes. The @giambattistavalliparis x @hm limited pre-drop is out 25 May. The main collection launches 7 November 2019.  #Project🖤
